---
import Layout from "../layouts/layouts.astro";
import MapEmbed from "../components/MapEmbed.astro";
---

<Layout title="Our House | Nardelli" currentPath={Astro.url.pathname}>
	<h1>Our House</h1>

	<section class="heroCard">
		<div class="introGrid">
			<div>
				<p>
					We hope you find everything you need for a comfortable stay at Nardelli. Clean bedsheets & towels should be folded on the beds (from the last guests). Beach towels (& beach toys for kids) are likely in the sitting room downstairs. In the kitchen cupboards and bathrooms you should find the usual basics easily.
				</p>

				<p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
					Kitchen equipment includes a large fridge, a gas hob, an air fryer, a microwave, a toaster, a kettle, and an Italian espresso maker (Moka pot).
				</p>
			</div>

			<img
				src="/photos/House.jpeg"
				alt="Nardelli"
				loading="lazy"
			/>
		</div>
	</section>

	<h2>Garden</h2>

<section class="subCard">
	<div class="subGrid">
		<div>
			<p>
				You can access the garden via the sitting room (keys either by the back door or with the keys by the front door), or through the garden gate at the front of the house.
			</p>
			<p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
				Outside there are tables and chairs, a clothes horse, sun loungers and a luxurios pool (a paddling pool called "Blue Baby") if you fancy a very local dip. It can be difficult to maintain the garden; if it’s dry, please water in the mornings or evenings if you can.
			</p>
		</div>

		<img
			src="/photos/Pool.jpeg"
			alt="Garden and pool"
			loading="lazy"
		/>
	</div>
</section>

	<h2>Rubbish bins &amp; recycling</h2>
	<p>
		We don’t have scheduled bin collections, so we tend to empty the bins daily and recycle bottles and other items as we go.
	</p>
	<p>
		We normally use the recycling and bins at the <strong>COOP supermarket</strong> or near the car park by <strong>Pescatore Cafe</strong> (these are good bins to use).
	</p>

	<h2>Neighbours</h2>
	<p>
		We have lots of lovely neighbours in Nardelli from different parts of Italy, the UK and the US. Please say hello — you can find names and locations on the map below.
	</p>

	<h2>Map</h2>
	<MapEmbed
		title="Nardelli – Our House & Neighbours"
		src="https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=17GPJ5eNXHo-2HNj_KNS6r1HLe_Nhqlc&ehbc=2E312F"
	/>

	<style>
		.heroCard {
			background: var(--card);
			border: 1px solid var(--border);
			border-radius: var(--radius);
			padding: 16px;
			margin: 12px 0 18px;
		}

		.introGrid {
			display: grid;
			gap: 16px;
			align-items: start;
		}

		.introGrid img {
			width: 100%;
			height: 260px;
			object-fit: cover;
			display: block;
			border-radius: calc(var(--radius) - 2px);
			border: 1px solid var(--border);
		}

		@media (min-width: 860px) {
			.introGrid {
				grid-template-columns: 1.25fr 0.75fr;
				align-items: center;
			}
			.introGrid img {
				height: 240px;
			}
		}

        .subCard {
	background: var(--card);
	border: 1px solid var(--border);
	border-radius: var(--radius);
	padding: 16px;
	margin: 10px 0 18px;
}

.subGrid {
	display: grid;
	gap: 16px;
	align-items: start;
}

.subGrid img {
	width: 100%;
	height: 240px;
	object-fit: cover;
	display: block;
	border-radius: calc(var(--radius) - 2px);
	border: 1px solid var(--border);
}

@media (min-width: 860px) {
	.subGrid {
		grid-template-columns: 1.25fr 0.75fr;
		align-items: center;
	}
	.subGrid img {
		height: 220px;
	}
}

	</style>
</Layout>